1. e4 e6 2. d4
{ In this chapter, we'll examine Black's sidelines on move 2, namely  2...c5, the most popular alternative to 2...d5 played more than 7000 times OTB  (350k+ online games)   2...b6, the 3rd most popular move with over 6000 OTB games  (270k+ online games)  .   and 2...a6, which has been played over 1000 times OTB  (40k+ online games)  . }
