{ 17...Re8  is met by another decisive sacrifice  18.Bxh6  !  18...gxh6  19.Qxh6  Threatening Qh8#  19...fxg6  20.Qxg6  Kf8  21.Qh6  Kg8  22.Qh7  Kf8  23.Bg6  Nc6  24.Qf7  Game over! }
18. Qxg6
{ White is not only threatening Bxh6 but also Qh7+ followed by Bg6 checkmate. Black has no defense.  Trying to block the bishop with   18...Rf5  fails to save Black  19.Nxa7  Qxa7  20.Bxh6  Bf8  21.Qxe6  Rf7  22.Qg6  There is no defense against Qh7 checkmate.   18...Rd8  leads to a forced mate after  19.Bxh6  Bf8  20.Qh7  Kf7  21.Bg6  Ke7  22.Bxg7  Nxb5  23.Bf6  Double-check and mate! }
