20. Rc1
{ With the idea Rc5. Black is objectively fine but he needs to play accurately to hold the balance. As in any sharp opening line, if Black knows 20+ computer moves he can reach a dynamically equal position. Nevertheless, this is not a draw. White has some initiative and Black needs to be precise. }
