Nxd4 Ne5 9. Nc3 a6
{ This is Black's best reply to 3. Bd3 and has been played well more than 40 times OTB  (>200 online games)  . }
10. Qe2 Nxf3+
{ We have now reached the mainline, where my main recommendation is the rare but very interesting11.gxf3. This move has only been played a few times OTB.  It has also featured in less than 10 online games. The players' average ratings were 2433 and White won 85% of the games. Despite this being a very limited sample size, it suggests that 11. gxf3 is not an easy move for Black to deal with.  We will examine the responses11...e5, 11...Nd5,11...Bb4 and finally we'll tackle11...Qc7.  I also cover the more popular, but less ambitious11.Qxf3 - an alternative variation best suited for lower-rated players or if you don't want to learn/remember as much theory. }
