{ This position occured later in the same game as the previous exercise. White's pieces are much more active but Black has just won a pawn with ...Qxa2. What is White's best move ? }
1. Bxg7 { Crashing through Black's kingside. } 1... Kxg7 2. Qf6+ Kg8 3. R1xd5
{ With Rg5 to follow. Black's king is toast. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
