[SetUp "1"]

{ This occurred later in the same game as the previous exercise. White managed to drive Black's king all the way to e7. How did White finish Black off ?    (Note: there is more than one move that wins)  . }
1. Rd7+ { An even faster way to finish the game is   1.Rxe6  fxe6  2.Qg7 } 1...
Bxd7 2. Qd6+
{ Black resigned as after  2...Kd8  3.Qxd7  is checkmate.  1-0 Hirneise, J  (2350)  - Engelhart, A  (2136)  Stuttgart 2017 }
