23... Bd5
{ Black wanted to block the d-file with this move. However, it is a big mistake. What did Black miss? }
24. Qxd5
{ A stunning queen sacrifice that illustrates how exposed Black's king on e8 is. }
24... exd5 25. Re1+ { The king has nowhere to go so } 25... Qe7 { is forced }
26. Rxe7+ Kd8 27. Nb7#
{ A beautiful way to end the game!   @@StartBracket@@this was all mentioned in the variation9...a6 #8 - informational  @@EndBracket@@ }
